t/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-and-band.-Credit-Semi-Song-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-and-band.-Credit-Semi-Song-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-and-band.-Credit-Semi-Song-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-and-band.-Credit-Semi-Song-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-and-band.-Credit-Semi-Song-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sturgill-simpson">斯特吉尔·辛普森 (Sturgill Simpson)</a>宣布以他的新艺名约翰尼·蓝天 (Johnny Blue Skies) 推出新专辑《Passage du Desir》。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sturgill-simpson-the-ballad-of-dood-juanita-review-3023596">斯特吉尔·辛普森（Sturgill Simpson）——《杜德与胡安妮塔之歌》评论：巧妙的声音叙事</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位音乐家的新时代是在他承诺以自己的名义只发行五张专辑之后到来的。 “这是斯特吉尔最后一张唱片。我总是说会有五个，我想知道我是否会反悔，”这位出生于肯塔基州的词曲作家在 2021 年宣传他的第五张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sturgill-simpson-the-ballad-of-dood-juanita-review-3023596">The Ballad of Dood &amp; Juanita</a> 》时告诉<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/sturgill-simpson-new-album-dood-juanita-1214449/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石杂志</em></a>。</p><p> 《Passage Du Desir》将于 7 月 12 日通过辛普森自己的独立唱片公司 High Top Mountain Records 发行。粉丝们可以<a href="https://fearofmusic.us10.list-manage.com/track/click?u=3679b0139839ec1ab0e40218c&amp;id=2d80689925&amp;e=6a0edec055" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里预购/预存</a>。</p><p>这张专辑由八首歌曲组成，由 Johnny Blue Skies 和 David Ferguson 制作，并在纳什维尔的 Clement House Recording Studio 和伦敦的 Abbey Road Studios 录制。 </p><figure id="attachment_3763365" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3763365" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3763365" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-Passage-Du-Desir-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="约翰尼·蓝天 (Johnny Blue Skies) 的《Passage Du Desir》专辑封面。信用出版社" width="2000" height="2007" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-Passage-Du-Desir-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-Passage-Du-Desir-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-Passage-Du-Desir-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x401.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-Passage-Du-Desir-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x803.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-Passage-Du-Desir-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x698.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-Passage-Du-Desir-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1397.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Johnny-Blue-Skies-Passage-Du-Desir-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1072.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3763365" class="wp-caption-text">约翰尼·蓝天 (Johnny Blue Skies) 的《Passage Du Desir》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>“Passage Du Desir”的曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>1.《悲伤沼泽》</strong><br /> <strong>2.《如果太阳不再升起》</strong><br /> <strong>3.《踏板车蓝调》</strong><br /> <strong>4.《木星的精灵》</strong><br /> <strong>5.《我是谁》</strong><br /> <strong>6.“正确的梦想”</strong><br /> <strong>7.“薄荷茶”</strong><br /> <strong>8.“一条路”</strong></p><p>辛普森此前在与<a href="/artists/diplo">Diplo</a>和 Dove Cameron 合作制作 2023 年曲目“Use Me (Brutal Hearts)”时使用了 Johnny Blue Skies 的绰号。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Diplo - Use Me（残酷之心）[官方视频]壮举。约翰尼·蓝天和德芙·卡梅隆" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_OX3uUhgusM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" 